OL,3,CFirst horse dies at Grand National
OL,4,CFestival moments after winning race
OL,6,FA horse has died during the Grand
OL,7,FNational Festival just moments after
OL,8,Fwinning its race in a "hollow victory".
OL,10,FGold Dancer suffered a fatal injury
OL,11,Fduring the William Hill Mildmay
OL,12,FNovices' Chase at Aintree after
OL,13,Flanding badly jumping the second fence
OL,14,Ffrom home.
OL,16,FHe stayed on his feet and kept going
OL,17,Fto win by four and three-quarter
OL,18,Flengths, but on pulling up it was soon
OL,19,Fclear the winner - who was 100-30
OL,20,Fjoint-favourite - had suffered a
OL,21,Fserious injury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
