CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775848268
OL,3,CFirst horse dies at Grand National
OL,4,CFestival moments after winning race
OL,6,F"It was an unbelievable performance,
OL,7,Fhe jumped brilliantly bar one little
OL,8,Fmistake.
OL,10,F"It's a hollow victory now, the poor
OL,11,Fhorse didn't deserve that."
OL,13,FThe death means a total of 68 horses
OL,14,Fhave now died at the Aintree Festival
OL,15,Fsince 2000, with figures from Animal
OL,16,FAid showing 17 horses have died after
OL,17,Fracing in the Grand National alone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@[O]
