PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775848268
OL,3,CFirst horse dies at Grand National
OL,4,CFestival moments after winning race
OL,6,FThe death has reinforced calls by
OL,7,Fanimal welfare charity the League
OL,8,FAgainst Cruel Sports for a public
OL,9,Fboycott and government intervention.
OL,11,FEmma Slawinski, chief executive at the
OL,12,FLeague Against Cruel Sports, said:
OL,13,F"Year after year we see horses dying
OL,14,Fat Aintree for people's entertainment
OL,15,Fand a cheap bet.
OL,17,F"Sadly, Gold Dancer is the latest
OL,18,Fvictim of this heartless spectacle
OL,19,Fwhich flies in the face of animal
OL,20,Fwelfare."
OL,26,@uD@AOU
